"<!-- pbc:A1 variant=split-half -->

# \\[Document title\\]

\\[Subtitle / engagement reference\\]

<!-- pbc:C4 variant=mission-statement -->

## About

\\[One-paragraph organizational summary tailored to this audience.\\]

<!-- pbc:A3 variant=question-list -->

Problem we are solving

- \\[Pain point 1 — concrete and measurable\\]
- \\[Pain point 2 — concrete and measurable\\]
- \\[Pain point 3 — concrete and measurable\\]

<!-- pbc:B1 variant=number-list -->

### \\[Solution component 1\\]

\\[How it addresses the problem above.\\]

### \\[Solution component 2\\]

\\[How it addresses the problem above.\\]

### \\[Solution component 3\\]

\\[How it addresses the problem above.\\]

<!-- pbc:C5 variant=stat-card -->

- **\\[KPI value\\]** Expected impact
- **\\[Weeks or months\\]** Timeline
- **\\[Headcount\\]** Team

<!-- pbc:D1 variant=simple-table -->

### Scope

| Label | Value |
| --- | --- |
| In scope | \\[Bullet 1, bullet 2\\] |
| Out of scope | \\[Bullet 1, bullet 2\\] |
| Assumptions | \\[Bullet 1, bullet 2\\] |

<!-- pbc:D2 variant=step-list -->

1. **Discovery** — \\[Goals and success criteria.\\]
2. **Design** — \\[Architecture and review gates.\\]
3. **Build** — \\[Iteration plan and demos.\\]
4. **Launch** — \\[Rollout and acceptance.\\]

<!-- pbc:E4 variant=policy-table -->

- **Shipping** \\[Delivery / hand-off terms\\]
- **Returns** \\[Revision / change-order policy\\]
- **Payment** \\[Milestones or schedule\\]
- **Confidentiality** \\[NDA reference\\]
"
`;

