"<section class="pbc-block pbc-A1 pbc-A1--full-bleed" data-block-id="A1"><div class="pbc-A1__inner"><h1 class="pbc-A1__headline">Ship faster. Stress less.</h1><p class="pbc-A1__tagline">The opinionated platform that turns your ideas into production in days, not months.</p><a class="pbc-A1__cta" href="/signup">Start free trial</a></div></section>

<section class="pbc-block pbc-A3" data-block-id="A3"><p class="pbc-A3__intro">If any of these sound familiar, you are in the right place.</p><ul class="pbc-A3__list"><li class="pbc-A3__point">Shipping a new feature takes weeks of plumbing work</li><li class="pbc-A3__point">Your CI is flaky and nobody owns it</li><li class="pbc-A3__point">Onboarding a new engineer costs a sprint</li></ul></section>

<section class="pbc-block pbc-B1 pbc-B1--icon-grid" data-block-id="B1"><ul class="pbc-B1__list"><li class="pbc-B1__item"><span class="pbc-B1__icon" aria-hidden="true">⚡</span><h3 class="pbc-B1__title">One-command setup</h3><p class="pbc-B1__desc">Go from clone to running in 60 seconds — no env shaming.</p></li><li class="pbc-B1__item"><span class="pbc-B1__icon" aria-hidden="true">📈</span><h3 class="pbc-B1__title">Built-in observability</h3><p class="pbc-B1__desc">Logs, traces, and metrics wired in by default. Find issues before customers do.</p></li><li class="pbc-B1__item"><span class="pbc-B1__icon" aria-hidden="true">🧭</span><h3 class="pbc-B1__title">Convention over configuration</h3><p class="pbc-B1__desc">Sane defaults that scale from prototype to production.</p></li></ul></section>

<section class="pbc-block pbc-C5 pbc-C5--stat-card" data-block-id="C5"><ul class="pbc-C5__list"><li class="pbc-C5__item"><span class="pbc-C5__value">2,400+</span><span class="pbc-C5__label">Teams shipping daily</span></li><li class="pbc-C5__item"><span class="pbc-C5__value">47<small>s</small></span><span class="pbc-C5__label">Average deploy time</span></li><li class="pbc-C5__item"><span class="pbc-C5__value">72</span><span class="pbc-C5__label">Customer NPS</span></li></ul></section>

<section class="pbc-block pbc-C1 pbc-C1--badge-row" data-block-id="C1"><ul class="pbc-C1__list"><li class="pbc-C1__item"><span class="pbc-C1__name">SOC 2 Type II</span><span class="pbc-C1__meta">AICPA · 2025</span></li><li class="pbc-C1__item"><span class="pbc-C1__name">ISO 27001</span><span class="pbc-C1__meta">ISO · 2024</span></li><li class="pbc-C1__item"><span class="pbc-C1__name">GDPR Ready</span><span class="pbc-C1__meta">EU</span></li></ul></section>

<section class="pbc-block pbc-E3 pbc-E3--accordion" data-block-id="E3"><div class="pbc-E3__list"><details class="pbc-E3__item"><summary>Is there a free tier?</summary><div class="pbc-E3__answer">Yes — every account starts on the free tier. No credit card required.</div></details><details class="pbc-E3__item"><summary>Can I self-host?</summary><div class="pbc-E3__answer">Enterprise plans include a self-hosted option with the same feature set.</div></details><details class="pbc-E3__item"><summary>How does pricing scale?</summary><div class="pbc-E3__answer">Pricing scales with active developers, not with usage spikes.</div></details></div></section>

<section class="pbc-block pbc-E1 pbc-E1--sticky-bottom" data-block-id="E1"><div class="pbc-E1__price-block"><span class="pbc-E1__price">$0</span></div><p class="pbc-E1__urgency">Cancel anytime. No credit card required.</p><a class="pbc-E1__cta" href="/signup">Start free trial</a></section>"
`;

exports[`WI-510 — preset × output snapshots > landing-saas — markdown snapshot 1`] = `
"<!-- pbc:A1 variant=full-bleed -->

# Ship faster. Stress less.

The opinionated platform that turns your ideas into production in days, not months.

[Start free trial](/signup)

<!-- pbc:A3 -->

If any of these sound familiar, you are in the right place.

- Shipping a new feature takes weeks of plumbing work
- Your CI is flaky and nobody owns it
- Onboarding a new engineer costs a sprint

<!-- pbc:B1 variant=icon-grid -->

### One-command setup

Go from clone to running in 60 seconds — no env shaming.

### Built-in observability

Logs, traces, and metrics wired in by default. Find issues before customers do.

### Convention over configuration

Sane defaults that scale from prototype to production.

<!-- pbc:C5 variant=stat-card -->

- **2,400+** Teams shipping daily
- **47s** Average deploy time
- **72** Customer NPS

<!-- pbc:C1 variant=badge-row -->

- **SOC 2 Type II** (AICPA · 2025)
- **ISO 27001** (ISO · 2024)
- **GDPR Ready** (EU)

<!-- pbc:E3 variant=accordion -->

**Is there a free tier?**

Yes — every account starts on the free tier. No credit card required.

**Can I self-host?**

Enterprise plans include a self-hosted option with the same feature set.

**How does pricing scale?**

Pricing scales with active developers, not with usage spikes.

<!-- pbc:E1 variant=sticky-bottom -->

**$0**

> Cancel anytime. No credit card required.

[Start free trial](/signup)
"
`;

